main event: A civilian telephone repairman observed two cigar-colored discs hovering over Hickam Air Force Base, spinning rapidly for about 2 minutes.
interesting points: The sighting occurred despite heavy air traffic and a large number of people present in the area,No additional witnesses were confirmed to have seen the objects,The discs were reported to be approximately 20 feet in size and shaped like cigars,The sighting was documented in the Project Blue Book records, The incident sparked an investigation by the Air Technical Intelligence Center.
